info.name: Snowflake Compute Pools API
info.description:
The Snowflake Compute Pools API is a REST API that you can use to access, update, and perform certain actions on Compute Pool resources.

Contact Support:
 Name: Snowflake, Inc.
 Email: support@snowflake.com

request.description: Fetch a compute pool using the SHOW command output.

response.name: successful
